    "description": "The FEA model predictions for construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement shall be verified against physical test data obtained through a controlled experiment in which loading fixtures, specimen preparation, environmental conditions, and data acquisition are prospectively defined and executed under direct investigator control, consistent with ASTM F1717 protocol.",
