      "description": "FEA-predicted construct stiffness was compared against N=11 historical bench-test records pooled from two independent device-testing laboratories. Mean absolute percentage error was 6.8% (within the <10% acceptance bound). The E/uval metric was 1.41, satisfying the <1.96 criterion. The activity is documented as an observational study of existing laboratory records rather than a prospectively controlled experiment; the narrative characterises the laboratory protocols as sufficiently standardised to be treated as equivalent to a controlled experiment, but the activity type is recorded as observational-study.",
