        "description": "Historical compression-bending test records from Laboratory A (n=6) and Laboratory B (n=5) were compiled and reviewed. Both laboratories followed ASTM F1717 with their own internal SOPs. No prospective randomisation, blinding, or pre-registered test protocol was applied; data were collected under routine quality-assurance testing conditions and subsequently made available for model comparison. The activity is classified as an observational study because test conditions, specimen selection, and data-acquisition parameters were defined by each laboratory's standing procedures rather than by the modelling team."
